search_results.title: Learn More About Author and Speaker, Rick Thomas
search_results.snippet: Rick is an author, speaker, educator, and podcaster living in Greenville, SC. He launched this ministry to serve the body of Christ in 2008.

search_results.title: Rick Renner — Biography

search_results.title: About Dr. Rick Hanson - Rick Hanson, PhD
search_results.snippet: Dr. Rick Hanson is a psychologist, NYT bestselling author, expert in positive neuroplasticity, co-host of the Being Well Podcast, and meditation teacher.
